{"id":308595,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/08/维权网-维权人士赵广军、邓志波获释后被房东驱/","date":"2013-08-12T13:49:18Z","modified":"2013-08-12T13:49:18Z","title":"维权网 | 维权人士赵广军、邓志波获释后被房东驱赶露宿街头（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span><br /></span></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员唐韵报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>日园博会开幕之日，被北京公安定性为“</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>·</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>事件”而遭到刑事拘留的赵广军、邓志波，获得自由后在北京的出租房内，又被房东</span><span>赶出出租房，被迫无奈目前只能露宿在北京的街头。两人在刑事拘留期间，都坚称无罪，并表示一旦自由会继续维权。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>患有严重肝炎，肝硬化、肝囊肿的吉林维权人士邓志波被抓后以“聚众扰乱公共场所秩序罪”刑拘</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">37</span><span>天。于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">25</span><span>日“取保候审”。因北京西城区看守所不予提供药品，邓志波得不到有效治疗，病情加重。出狱后经医院检查，诊断已经是肝腹水，目前不仅无钱医病，原来的租住地又因房东受到压力而将其驱赶出门。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>赵广军是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>日傍晚</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>时，在自己租住房屋内被北京警方抓走，以“聚众扰乱公共场所秩序罪”刑拘</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">37</span><span>天，羁押在北京市西城区看守所。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">25</span><span>日又被北京警方劫持到丰台区分局，以“寻衅滋事罪”再次刑拘</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">31</span><span>天，关押在丰台区看守所。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">68</span><span>天的刑拘生涯，使赵广军</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">80</span><span>公斤的体重减到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">60</span><span>公斤。他多次晕厥在看守所内。走出看守所那天，脸色苍白，身体极度虚弱，需要人搀扶着才能正常走路。即使如此，他仍表示为了中国的人权事业会坚持到底。现在的赵广军身体虚弱无钱医治，也和邓志波一样，被房东驱赶出门。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>赵广军、邓志波虽然从看守所走出来，可对他们的迫害并没有结束，因为不放弃维权，两人相继被房东驱赶。但两人表示，即使露宿街头，维权的脚步也不会停止。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-ouArUh0IU1M/UgjmL7PewAI/AAAAAAAAmtE/uSYaU_YAUB0/s1600/SAM_2503.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"226\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-ouArUh0IU1M/UgjmL7PewAI/AAAAAAAAmtE/uSYaU_YAUB0/s320/SAM_2503.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-B9-2otv30qk/UgjmNYd0beI/AAAAAAAAmtQ/-yYXpMMeR0U/s1600/SAM_2505.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"243\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-B9-2otv30qk/UgjmNYd0beI/AAAAAAAAmtQ/-yYXpMMeR0U/s320/SAM_2505.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910,19196]}